overview.en: Ant array, or ATA for short, is a new global ecosystem based on blockchain construction in the game industry. It will overturn the traditional rules of the game, link up the entire game ecological chain in the decentralized structure of block chain, and realize storage and circulation. ATA provides intelligent contracts for global game developers to realize the integration and collaboration between the in-game economic system and ATA economic system.
overview.zh: 蚁阵Ant array，简称ATA，ATA是一个立足于游戏产业基于区块链构建的新型全球生态体系。它将颠覆传统的游戏规则，在区块链去中心化的结构中将整个游戏生态链链接起来，实现存储和流通。ATA面向全球游戏开发者提供智能合约，实现游戏内经济体系和ATA经济体系的打通与协同。
